The Data Mining method we used was Clustering. Clustering was used to take several statisical categories and set them with other examples with similar stats. For example, the city demograpahic problem dealt with 40 cities and their demogrpahics in 5 different categories. 
First all the stats were entered into excel.
2nd -  they were standarized using standard deviation and means to get comparable and measureable numbers.
3rd - we used VLOOKUP to index all the cities and make 4 city cluster centers
4th - we used SUMXmy2 to get each city a comparable minimum to compare 
5th  - using the 4 clusters city centers each city was set to a cluster that was similar in numbers found
